title: Hill Street Cafe and Coffee House
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Local coffee house and cafe restaurant situated in a house building. Extensive food menu includes some vegetarian and vegan dishes, marked on the menu. Organic coffee served. Casual seating in the back patio and in enclosed deck. Also an art gallery upstairs.
